<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Phish Directory!</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Welcome to Phish Directory, the community-driven database of phishing URLs.">
  <meta name="author" content="Phish Directory">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      margin: 40px auto;
      max-width: 600px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: white;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      margin-top: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      display: block;
    }
    .main-heading {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #55625c;
      margin: 16px 0;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #55625c;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .divider {
      border: 1px solid #83bab4;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .content {
      margin-top: 32px;
    }
    .text {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #55625c;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .feature-list {
      list-style: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .feature-list li {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #55625c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .button-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    .button {
      background-color: #83bab4;
      color: white;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .open-source-box {
      background-color: #f5f7f7;
      border-left: 4px solid #83bab4;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 32px 0;
    }
    .open-source-heading {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #55625c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .open-source-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #55625c;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .section-heading {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #55625c;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .link {
      color: #83bab4;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .link-bold {
      color: #83bab4;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .signature {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #55625c;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .footer-divider {
      border: 1px solid #cbac91;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #55625c;
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header with Logo -->
    <div class="header">
      <%= image_tag "https://s3.hogwarts.dev/assets/phishdirectory.jpeg",
                    alt: "Phish Directory Logo",
                    class: "logo" %>
      <h1 class="main-heading">Welcome to Phish Directory</h1>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider">

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p class="text">
        Hi <%= @user.first_name %>! Thank you for joining Phish Directory, the community-driven database of phishing URLs.
      </p>

      <p class="text">
        At Phish Directory, our mission is to help you stay safe from phishing attacks by providing you with the latest information on phishing URLs. With your participation, we can build a stronger defense against cyber threats.
      </p>

      <p class="text">
        Here's what you can do with Phish Directory:
      </p>

      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>Report suspicious URLs to our database</li>
        <li>Verify if a URL has been reported as phishing</li>
        <li>Stay updated on the latest phishing trends</li>
        <li>Contribute to a safer internet for everyone</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="button-section">
        <%= link_to "Access Your Dashboard",
                    "https://phish.directory/dashboard",
                    class: "button" %>
      </div>

      <!-- Open Source Feature Box -->
      <div class="open-source-box">
        <h2 class="open-source-heading">ðŸ”§ We're open source!</h2>
        <p class="open-source-text">
          Interested in helping develop Phish Directory API? Join our Slack and let us know or email
          <%= link_to "devrel@phish.directory",
                      "mailto:devrel@phish.directory",
                      class: "link-bold" %>.
          We welcome contributors of all skill levels to help make our project even better.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="section-heading">Join Our Community</h2>

      <p class="text">
        You'll receive an invitation to our Community Slack within the next 10 minutes. If you don't see it, please check your spam folder. Still having trouble? Email
        <%= link_to "slack@phish.directory",
                    "mailto:slack@phish.directory",
                    class: "link" %>
        for assistance.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-heading">Share Your Work</h2>

      <p class="text">
        We'd love to see what you create with Phish Directory! Send your projects, tools, or integrations to
        <%= link_to "showcase@phish.directory",
                    "mailto:showcase@phish.directory",
                    class: "link" %>
        and we might feature your work in our community highlights.
      </p>

      <h2 class="section-heading">Need Help?</h2>

      <p class="text">
        If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at
        <%= link_to "support@phish.directory",
                    "mailto:support@phish.directory",
                    class: "link" %>.
      </p>

      <p class="signature">
        Stay vigilant,<br>
        The Phish Directory Team
      </p>
    </div>

    <hr class="footer-divider">

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p class="footer-text">Â© 2025 Phish Directory. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
